data.description: New construction to be complete Summer 2020, 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home in Oak Grove Meadows, a beautiful community situated on gently winding, sidewalk lined streets, features include walking paths and common area playground.. Located in the Howell Public School District. RESNET ENERGY SMART NEW CONSTRUCTION, 10 YEAR STRUCTURAL WARRANTY. One of our newest floor plans welcome's you home to a space that fits all your needs with over 2000 sq ft of finished living space. The main floor features a dining nook and kitchen that opens to a large great room, all with vaulted ceilings to give you a very open space. Kitchen features granite counters and tile backsplash. The master bedroom features a huge WIC and private full bath and finishes the upper main level. Walkout lower level has over 900 finished sq ft and includes a large rec room, 2 spacious bedrooms, with daylight windows, and a full bath to complete the living space.Patio creates an outdoor space. Garage is dry-walled and taped.
